{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 241032,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　認識の甘さが招いたことですね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This is something brought about by a lack of awareness.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241033,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もっと何か対策は打てなかったのか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Couldn't they have taken more countermeasures,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241034,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　政府の怠慢がこういった状況を許したんですよねぇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " the government's negligence allowed this kind of situation to happen.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241035,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そもそも私が思うにですね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"In the first place, I think that...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241036,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お母さん、お母さーーん！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Mom, Mom---!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241037,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんか難波ですごい事件起きてるよ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Something really big is happening in Namba!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241038,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああうん、見てた見てた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, yeah, I was watching it."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241039,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　近いわよねぇ、怖いわぁ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " It's close, isn't it? Scary...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241040,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あんた、今日は外に出たら駄目よ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You shouldn't go outside today, okay?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241041,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「この人達、いったいなんなんだろうね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Who exactly are these people?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241042,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　テロリストらしいけど、格好が変すぎ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " They seem to be terrorists, but their outfits are way too strange.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241043,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これあんたが好きな、ほら、あれ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This is like what you like, you know, that,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241044,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ピコピコの中の服装みたいよねぇ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " the kind of clothes inside the 'Pico Pico,' right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241045,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ね？　コスプレみたいだよね〜」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"See? Looks like cosplay, right?~\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241046,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「テレビの中でも正体は分かってないって言ってるよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even on TV, they say they don't know who they really are."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241047,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　剣を振り回して、魔法まで使ったんだって」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " They even waved swords around and used magic.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241048,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えー、そんなまさかぁ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh— no way!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241049,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「外国のすごい機関？　とかが作ってる最新の武器とかよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Some foreign powerful agency? They must have made the latest weapons."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241050,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ＭＡＳＡ？　が作ってるのよ、きっと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " MASA? It's definitely made by them.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241051,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はあ〜、とにかく怖いわぁ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Haah~, anyway, it's really scary."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241052,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あんたも気をつけるのよ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " You be careful too, okay?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241053,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は〜い」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Okaaaay.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241054,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "テレビの中ではコメンテーターの面々が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Inside the TV, the commentators"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241055,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "順番に無責任な感想を垂れ流していた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " were irresponsibly spouting their impressions one after another."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241056,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その中、メインキャスターの顔色が変わる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Among them, the main newscaster's expression changed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241057,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、ちょっとすみません。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, excuse me for a moment."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241058,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　続報が来ました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " We have a breaking update.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241059,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「政府は今回の一件をテロ行為だと断定。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The government has determined that this incident is an act of terrorism."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241060,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あっ、これは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Oh, this is...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241061,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「特警の出動を許可したとのことです！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"They have authorized the Special Police to be deployed!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241062,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「がーーー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Gaaahhhh!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241063,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんでこんなことになっとるんじゃー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Why is it turning out like this?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241064,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はひ……はひ……疲れました……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hah... hah... I'm tired...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241065,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス達は丸一日戦い続けて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and the others had been fighting all day long,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241066,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "既に疲労困憊になっていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and were already utterly exhausted."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241067,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "現在は付近の学校に乗り込み、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They had now taken refuge in a nearby school,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241068,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "敵から隠れて籠城作戦に出ていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " hiding from enemies and started a siege defense strategy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241069,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「わけの分からん奴らが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"These incomprehensible guys"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241070,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ワラワラと湧いてきて……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " have swarmed all over the place..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241071,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この世界は一体どうなってんだ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " What on earth is happening to this world...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241072,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「どうしよう、健太郎くん……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What should we do, Kentaro-kun..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241073,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私達、国家反逆罪になってしまった」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " We've now been charged with high treason.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241074,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「大丈夫、カメラにうつってないから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's okay, we aren't on camera,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241075,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ワルイのはランスさんだけ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " only Rance-san is the bad one.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241076,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アホか！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You idiot!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241077,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「大して悪いことしてないのに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We didn't do anything that bad,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241078,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いきなり襲ってきやがって……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " yet they suddenly attacked us..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241079,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　交渉力もなにもない野蛮な連中だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " They're savage people with no negotiation skills or anything.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241080,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「悪いことしてない……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We didn't do anything wrong...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241081,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うう、ここにいた女子学生さん達に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh, to the female students here,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241082,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　色々とひどいことしてたような……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " it seems we've done some terrible things...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241083,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「俺は紳士的に口説こうとしただけだぞ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I only tried to flirt with them politely."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241084,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それをきゃーきゃー逃げ回るから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " But because they ran away screaming,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241085,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あんなことになるのだ、がははは！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " it turned out like that, gahahaha!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241086,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それ以前に最初に出会った方々を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even before that, defeating the people we first encountered"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241087,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　倒したのがいけなかったのかも知れません」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " might have been a mistake.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241088,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふん、あんなん夜盗みたいなもんだろ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph, those guys are like night thieves."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241089,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　むしろ殺すのが正義だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Killing them is justice, frankly.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241090,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「とにかく少々まずいですね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Anyway, this is somewhat bad.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241091,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「軍隊の動きが異様に迅速です……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The army's movements are unusually swift...\""
    }
  ]
}

